body.name: lamphle Bathroom Wall Cabinet, Wall Mount Kitchen Bathroom Organizer Countertop Floating Wall Shelves No Drill Self Adhesive, 2 Tier Bedroom Storage Shelves for Vent Doors, Over Toilet, White White
features: 💧[ Cosmetics Organizer ] - Featuring multi-grid tiers and spacious desktop design, this bathroom storage cabinet will be the perfect choice for you if you are looking for something to organize your cosmetics.
💧[ Floating Design ] - Not just for storing different kinds of items, this simple silhouette and hollow flower pattern storage cabinet also can be used as a nice home decoration.

💧[ High-quality Waterproof ] - Modern bathroom storage rack is made of WPC to make the structure more stable. The surface of the cabinet is coated with a special waterproof coating, which makes the surface smooth and flat, and easy to clean.

💧[ Easy to Install ] - The wall-mounted bathroom cabinet is very easy to install, with detailed installation instructions to guide you through installation, and each panel and small parts are numbered for clear identification.

💧[ Multi-purpose & Space Saving ] - Multifunctional wall-mounted storage cabinet is designed to improve space utilization in your apartments. It attaches tightly to the wall and can be mounted above a vanity or toilet to make full use of the vertical space without taking up valuable floor space. This bathroom cabinet is the best storage solution for small spaces, perfect for bathrooms, kitchens, or bedrooms.
